==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Indiscriminate
<hw>In`dis*crim"i*nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
discriminate; wanting discrimination; undistinguishing; not making any
distinction; confused; promiscuous.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Blind or
<xex>indiscriminate</xex> forgiveness.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>I.
Taylor.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>indiscriminate</qex> defense of right and wrong.</q>
<rj><qau>Junius.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>In`dis*crim"i*nate*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>Cowper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Indiscriminating</ent>⟦br⟧
